profile:
Highrise Service Group was born in April of 2020 after finding a lack of professional services designed specifically for those who live in condominiums and apartment buildings. Not to say that these services didn't already exist, we found that four major things were missing:

1. Proper Training: We've invested highly in the training of our cleaning specialist and in the products they use. Keeping both our staff and clients in mind, we use both eco friendly and biodegradable products.

2. Security: We've implemented security measures to keep your mind at ease. Our specialists are background checked, are always in uniform and carry an ID badge with their name, position and a security code that will verify their Identity and clean criminal record.

3. Technology: Our online scheduler and customer dashboard allows our clients to make changes to their bookings 24/7. Although we've added technology to our services, we still have a phone number that will be answered by a human, not a robot.

4. Insurance: Keeping your property and it's belongings safe. We're happy to say that our services are insured, bonded and our staff is covered by WSIB. Keeping your mind at ease.

HOW WE'RE DIFFERENT
At Highrise Service group, we've tailored our services specifically for those who reside in condos and apartment buildings.

Upfront Costs
We've all been on the other end of a sales call or even taken time out of our day to schedule an at-home estimate. At HSG, our pricing is listed directly on our booking form, fully transparent with no hidden fees.

Pay Securely Online
Our stress free services include never having to go to the bank or writing us a cheque. Our encrypted online scheduling system will automatically charge the card on file once your cleaning is completed.

No Contracts
Our services have no end date and can be canceled at any time. All we ask is for 24 hours notice if you need to make any changes.

Locally Owned
We are proudly Canadian! Locally owned & managed in Ottawa, ON.
products: We use eco friendly & biodegradable products. Ensuring the safety of both our clients and our staff members. Products and equipment included at no extra cost.
